&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In Christianity, what is the biggest sin of Adam and Eve?  &lt;br&gt;
They ate the fruit of knowledge.  &lt;br&gt;
The Forbidden fruit.  &lt;br&gt;
Because of this knowledge, they became aware of their human nature  &lt;br&gt;
Following that, they knew their limitation, their emotion, and feeling  &lt;br&gt;
They became shy and covered their bodies.  &lt;br&gt;
This led to their sex life,  &lt;br&gt;
And because of sex, progeny happened.  &lt;br&gt;
And we humans are the creation of that.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
