We do some actions on the given input  &lt;br&gt;
And we produce some output  &lt;br&gt;
Input is never 100% in our control. But, the quantity and quality of the benefits  &lt;br&gt;
depends upon how the output of a process  &lt;br&gt;
is perceived by the receiver.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
